<li><i>American Muslims: Bridging Faith and Freedom</i> by <a href="/wiki/M._A._Muqtedar_Khan" title="M. A. Muqtedar Khan">M. A. Muqtedar Khan</a>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Charles_Kurzman" title="Charles Kurzman">Charles Kurzman</a>, ed. (1998). <i>Liberal Islam: A Sourcebook</i>. Oxford University Press, USA. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-19-511622-4" title="Special:BookSources/0-19-511622-4">0-19-511622-4</a>.</li>
